    "'<id>\\t<canonical>' for each; the SAME static aarch64 binary runs on BOTH sides of the differential.",
    "'arch_expected' documents the architecturally-defined result (human review + self-test synthesis).",
    "It is NOT the differential oracle: diff_corpus.py compares the qemu-TCG SUT run against the",
    "INDEPENDENT real-ARM64 reference run and never consults arch_expected (plan §5 WA.2; W0.4 DoD #4).",
    "'binds_translation_manifest_sha256' pins the exact reviewed WA.2 manifest bytes; coverage_report.py",
    "fails closed if it does not match sha256(translation-validation-manifest.json)."
  ],
