      "that entry's output ONLY (flip bit 0). The reference set is never mutated. A correct harness then",
      "reports: all real tests match (good corpus passes) AND the seed entry mismatches (seeded mismatch",
      "detected). A harness that fails to flag the seed is INVALID (plan §3 W0.4; §5 WA.2)."
    ],
    "mutation": "flip bit 0 of the seed entry's 64-bit result on the SUT side only"
  },
